檢疫措施，或聚集限制等有一定空間調整。他強調，具體仍要由專家審視，先作政策行政上考慮。<br />\n<br />\n政府重申，「安心出行」流動應用程式不涉及市民做登記，<span class=\"red\">使用者的出行記錄只存放在自己的手機，個人行蹤不會外泄，不構成私穩風險。</span><br />\n<br />\n邊個話唔使嘟架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n幾撚勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n登記過嘅資料只儲存係自己電話<br />\n但我確診左 其他人又會收到通知"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T09:09:12.000Z","msg":"呢種structure其實做到<br />\n<br />\n問題係呢個誠信已經破產嘅衙門肯定唔止咁簡單<br />\n人哋叫你開sourcecode就淨係識耍太極"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T10:02:44.000Z","msg":"真心想學野 睇隔離post(自己無裝過）<br />\n話個尻apps咩都唔洗登記 唔洗登記個apps點知確診係我？<br />\n直接拎確診個人部電話 然後開佢個apps?"},{"pid":"25ebc9a0090169236e14cc98291597327337f61a","tid":2412803,"uid":25794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2fef09415461eec05e7d695737af5ab9755dcdc7","tid":2412803,"uid":254450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13ad2cb1b7df8ea93396462a0e28f2deb80e9664","tid":2412803,"uid":182830,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T08:59:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o7sSOm6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo7sSOm6.jpg&h=c64aec75&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n憲報話外賣除外喎!"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T09:16:04.000Z","msg":"依家d政府嘢自己人都跟唔切啦，上晝度完橋咨詢都唔使第二日就話行，行咗再算，有甩漏就再改改到啱為止，做嘢完全冇plan仲衰過d幾人公司仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T10:50:46.000Z","msg":"D 蚊型公司都有個腦細可以揸fit 話事<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a568b4615f8675017cdfc9020c7fd81d75ad00e5","tid":2412803,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07a9c22542546864603ded650b0a6404ee35ee6f","tid":2412803,"uid":56790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35be6aa52a4165474fde056ec13d69226da62190","tid":2412803,"uid":